name: e India Insurance
overview: e India Insurance is a pioneer in offering Indian insurance policies online so that the customer can purhcase using a credit card, debit card or a cheque. We have provided online services to over 20,000 satisfied customers so far. At EIndiaInsurance, we have developed user friendly web tools to help customers make an informed decision while purchasing online insurance. We provide an extensive listing of available Indian insurance policies and have developed an “insurance comparison” tool. This tool provides the user with free insurance quotes and allows the customer to compare insurance plans based on the user input. This comparison facility also allows customer to view policy brochures, compare in detail a few selected insurance policies and even buy the policies directly using a credit card.
